Package com.orientechnologies.common.concur.lock

Class OOneEntryPerKeyLockManager<T>

java.lang.Object
com.orientechnologies.common.concur.lock.OOneEntryPerKeyLockManager<T>
Type Parameters:
T - Type of keys
All Implemented Interfaces:
OLockManager<T>
public class OOneEntryPerKeyLockManager<T> extends Object implements OLockManager<T>
Original Lock Manager implementation that uses a concurrent linked hash map to store one entry per key. This could be very expensive in case the number of locks are a lot.
Author:
Luca Garulli (l.garulli--(at)--orientdb.com)
